2010-12-08 Theodore Papadopoulo <Theodore.Papadopoulo@sophia.inria.fr>
	* manual/makeHTMLIndex.cpp: Convert ro modern C++.

2010-12-08 Theodore Papadopoulo <Theodore.Papadopoulo@sophia.inria.fr>
	* doc/doxygen/Doxyfile.in: Use pdflatex.
	* doc/Makefile.am: Update

