	* examples/erf.cpp, examples/qcd.cpp: Fixed header declaration to ISO
	  standard C++ and added missing using namespace declaration.

2010-05-26 Theodore Papadopoulo <Theodore.Papadopoulo@sophia.inria.fr>
	* configure.ac: Correct a typo on the FULLY64BIT define.

2010-02-09  Patrik Jonsson <code@familjenjonsson.org>

